{"tid":388913,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解英國人啲中文名咁好聽？","createTime":"2017-09-05T18:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T23:51:27.000Z","uid":60344,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23475da5f79e9268f71a2ef418d45fb6a41023f9","tid":388913,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T18:50:45.000Z","msg":"係邊個幫佢地改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n文翠珊、貝利雅、彭定康⋯⋯<br />\n仲有一大堆港督大班：<br />\n砵甸乍（呢個麻麻）、楊慕琦、李嘉誠、以律、渣甸（霸氣盡現）、嘉道理、衛奕信、摩地、盧嘉、柏立基、白文信、摩利臣（麻麻地）⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知係邊個改？<br />\n漢學家？"},{"pid":"3496bfa79483d1761ce550add2f8aedc50076ae5","tid":388913,"uid":31254,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:21:04.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30dbf1a4ea3a4dd061516afc6af69a6778be00a7","tid":388913,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"馬份"},{"pid":"4c06dfbcd5943fd834e02cbdb74918c67a57172e","tid":388913,"uid":72730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:44:25.000Z","msg":"「<em>那時候，英國人中文譯名這事由港英政府「中文公事管理局」（1996年改組為「法定語文事務署」），同英國駐港商務專員公署等官方機構共同制定。</em>」<br />\n另外有d自己讀漢學, d漢學老師或者佢自己改"},{"pid":"5a7d228f749614e5b2a88abe100898f7d61ded99","tid":388913,"uid":72730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:44:37.000Z","msg":"夏文達<br />\n霍理林<br />\n卓慧思<br />\n房應麟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc36e2b26bcb9d0c5d4809755285dc1362c51bb","tid":388913,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:35:00.000Z","msg":"莫雷拉"},{"pid":"8b4f60099d1809c9f4b7e82841d4efcee328648f","tid":388913,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"街名都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c