17-09-06T23:13:52.000Z","msg":"馬卓安<br />\n文立彬<br />\n文禮彬<br />\n咁多個名我覺得楊慕琦改得最好<br />\nMark Young 又啱位又啱音又夠文雅"},{"pid":"aa811a384d34954fc7c032a95723299c13f51561","tid":388913,"uid":59140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「<em>那時候，英國人中文譯名這事由港英政府「中文公事管理局」（1996年改組為「法定語文事務署」），同英國駐港商務專員公署等官方機構共同制定。</em>」<br />\n另外有d自己讀漢學, d漢學老師或者佢自己改</blockquote><br />\n依家係英國駐港澳大使館改"},{"pid":"35d38f7af3fd7293affdde114f49108dd5536eed","tid":388913,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:57:54.000Z","msg":"戴麟趾 堅尼地 砵甸乍呢啲都唔見得好聽"},{"pid":"4ca9199d86379293b8588ac76bd13e1221be1afd","tid":388913,"uid":6864,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴麟趾 堅尼地 砵甸乍呢啲都唔見得好聽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話戴麟趾唔好係因為你唔識啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n戴麟趾出自《詩經‧周南》，有後代良善興盛之意。「麟之趾」篇曰：「麟之趾，振振公子，于嗟麟兮。」「關睢序」曰：「然則關雎麟趾之化，王者之風，故系之周公。」周文王子孫繁衍，後人用麟趾呈祥來恭賀人家添丁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/blogs/sandwich/%E6%B4%8B%E5%AE%98%E6%BC%A2%E5%90%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B3%E6%B2%BB%E6%BC%A2%E6%B0%91-014943879.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fblogs%2Fsandwich%2F%25E6%25B4%258B%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%2590%258D%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E6%25B0%2591-014943879.html&d=KD%2FBXRQF1n%2F%2FQhBJth2bkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2caffe38\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/blogs/sandwich/%E6%B4%8B%E5%AE%98%E6%BC%A2%E5%90%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B3%E6%B2%BB%E6%BC%A2%E6%B0%91-014943879.html</a>"},{"pid":"498339546d6e75dabe116e053a11e6d18012a93c","tid":388913,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戴麟趾 堅尼地 砵甸乍呢啲都唔見得好聽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話戴麟趾唔好係因為你唔識啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n戴麟趾出自《詩經‧周南》，有後代良善興盛之意。「麟之趾」篇曰：「麟之趾，振振公子，于嗟麟兮。」「關睢序」曰：「然則關雎麟趾之化，王者之風，故系之周公。」周文王子孫繁衍，後人用麟趾呈祥來恭賀人家添丁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/blogs/sandwich/%E6%B4%8B%E5%AE%98%E6%BC%A2%E5%90%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B3%E6%B2%BB%E6%BC%A2%E6%B0%91-014943879.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fblogs%2Fsandwich%2F%25E6%25B4%258B%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%2590%258D%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E6%25B0%2591-014943879.html&d=KD%2FBXRQF1n%2F%2FQhBJth2bkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2caffe38\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/blogs/sandwich/%E6%B4%8B%E5%AE%98%E6%BC%A2%E5%90%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B3%E6%B2%BB%E6%BC%A2%E6%B0%91-014943879.html</a></blockquote><br />\n以前d人真係有文化修養 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}